experiment HMZ_RU
instrument TRO
start 2010 11 12 1200
end 2010 11 12 1700
status R
description Contrasting O/X-mode HF heater effects in the magnetic zenith 
contact Nataly Blagoveshchenskaya
phone +7-812-337-3191
